{"tid":1738030,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"路上種釘嘅手足，停一停先","createTime":"2019-11-19T06:21:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T06:46:26.000Z","uid":264782,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c5f43ad8514e55b678ab176669a5066e8cd853f2","tid":1738030,"uid":264782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:21:22.000Z","msg":"11月17、18兩晚，見有手足逃走時釘到腳（油麻地），請嗰啲在馬路上膠邊種釘嘅手足停一停先！足足兩晚，都見有手足踩中！！<br />\n狗嘅命係垃圾，唔理有幾多狗、狗車中釘，都賠唔返因為踩中釘而受傷跌倒甚至被捕嘅手足！！<br />\n慌亂中見路就跑，好多手足根本聽唔到其他人提「唔好踩釘」‼️ 手足嘅鞋唔同狗鞋，根本頂唔住‼️<br />\n種釘嘅壞處絕對比好處大，我們手足一個都不能少‼️請不要種釘‼️"},{"pid":"15907caedc2a2f867342b4912566ea6825e52d45","tid":1738030,"uid":340080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:23:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nfPj0o6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnfPj0o6.jpg&h=9a6569f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b93759db3cdf68e1a0e41072d70f096e7293439e","tid":1738030,"uid":33939,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:24:43.000Z","msg":"叫咗唔好啦，一走就實自己人中。"},{"pid":"691c7428a0d70da6af9681fb176fbe1442da3710","tid":1738030,"uid":224857,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:25:18.000Z","msg":"佢地d鞋應該防釘，好似安全鞋咁。唔好俾人帶方向"},{"pid":"31b05eef595e806303763279b31481ce1d9d1d2e","tid":1738030,"uid":224857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:25:52.000Z","msg":"佢地d鞋應該防釘，好似安全鞋咁。唔好俾人帶方向"},{"pid":"1015a270378d3886a1d98db11c41bd473b73c17a","tid":1738030,"uid":224857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:26:04.000Z","msg":"佢地d鞋應該防釘，好似安全鞋咁。唔好俾人帶方向"},{"pid":"e1bb1342a38fdb67b0c40e0d23560a7ae97dc131","tid":1738030,"uid":224857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:26:14.000Z","msg":"佢地d鞋應該防釘，好似安全鞋咁。唔好俾人帶方向"},{"pid":"2419c5a51185306c6678f58ad27a71c20a197676","tid":1738030,"uid":224857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:26:25.